oppenheim 20 was charged with fourthdegree criminal mischief and 
thirddegree falsely reporting an incident 
oppenheim a junior was president of the jewish student union 
when slurs and swastikas a symbol used by nazi germany were 
painted on the groups office and sanctuary on nov 10 1988 it was 
the eve of the 50th anniversary of kristallnacht the night nazi 
stormtroopers began their reign of terror against german jews by 
smashing up their stores and homes 
oppenheim was quoted at the time as condemning the act as 
horrible and hurtful he also speculated the vandalism was a 
calculated political act 
