including a member of the public the program now is limited to 
lenders that voluntarily agree to participate 
the boards have the authority to review mortgages to make sure 
there is no geographic discrimination in lending practices 
the legislative package would also place mortgage companies 
mortgage brokers and all parties making five or more mortgage loans 
a year under the specific licensing and examination powers of the 
division of banks 
mortgage companies a fastgrowing segment of the financial 
services industries now are not regulated by the state consumer 
affairs secretary mary ann walsh has made their regulation a 
priority issue on her legislative agenda 
